  1143→  1143→      shake:/shake|meal\s*prep|morning\s*meal/i,
  1144→  1144→      protein:/protein\s*[\:✓\s]*(\d+)g?|(\d+)g\+?\s*protein/i,
  1145→  1145→      calories:/calorie|kcal|calories\s*[\:✓]/i,
